    summary: "Several profiles for \"Sameer Mohammad\" on GitHub and related professional platforms indicate experience in React, Node, Full Stack, and Software Engineering roles.\n\nOne prominent profile describes Sameer Mohammad as building data systems and modern web applications, with a focus on data engineering, analytics, and full stack development[1]. This individual\'s experience includes roles as a Full Stack Engineer and Software Engineer. As a Full Stack Engineer, they built and maintained EMR platform modules using technologies like React, Next.js, Node.js, and NestJS. In a Software Engineer role, they developed CRM platform features utilizing React, TypeScript, and Node.js[1].\n\nAnother \"Sameer Mohammad\" is associated with Full Stack Academy, where their listed skills include HTML, CSS, Bootstrap, JavaScript, and React.js[2]. Additionally, a \"Sameer Mohammad\" is listed as an \"AWS Azure Devops Engineer\" and is also generally associated with \"Full Stack React JS Developer\" roles[3].\n\nSources:\n[1] [sameerion.com](https://vertexaisearch.cloud.google.com/grounding-api-redirect/AUZIYQHTO-7uqdeWPYBBQYjPA2BxBC_ciTnVDlbdcT6VbWxZ5l0mx1oKK6pYvU6D5za2NZdQYM-ynu-7D59V3dJPIak-jxyXOGwjKzCf9G04GMBSM_0znmg1)\n[2] [fullstackacademy.in](https://vertexaisearch.cloud.google.com/grounding-api-redirect/AUZIYQEFwH0nR2tCRRvVQDYf6AW3QTOsQPiQ7FrtpXHJ0qmh93o434C4Y7EEk4eLQBSc357_FwmZlExa4-eS2oeuAbShCfAqGvk2m4kaFb9qZ6OsIvYxQYlSHxpvZ0yIq7W1bzQPZcJMSLYR0e0zzjHr4hpgD9mvPbceIy1JD7pSB3VdHmCCFZGUajICrOqVDbvOQ3MSbjQct_j6)\n[3] [nvoids.com](https://vertexaisearch.cloud.google.com/grounding-api-redirect/AUZIYQGP0KVOdY5tU4PObo38qWPgmy2S2ncz02uRupCPfG9sxSIZeqALGZU-Oke5ed4lD9T87V7O-2WWWCFNjVUfAiVGp6PIRGxjC3gcE5m3fXGjVYJ0PDUskVfDDQ==)"
