    summary: "The search for \"Sameer Mohammad\" on wayup.com and bebee.com did not yield any direct results from those specific platforms. The search results provided information about several individuals named Sameer Mohammad from other websites.\n\nBased on the broader search, here are some individuals named Sameer Mohammad:\n\n*   **Sameer Mohammad (Research)**: A Principal Investigator at King Abdullah International Medical Research Center, with research interests in insulin resistance and metabolic homeostasis. He also has a Google Scholar profile listing his publications.[1][2]\n*   **Sameer F. Mohammad (Instructor)**: An instructor in the Electrical Engineering Department at the United Arab Emirates University (UAEU). His areas of interest include power system operation and optimization, power system restructuring, reactive power pricing, control, and electrical machines.[3]\n*   **Sameer F. Mohammad (Attorney)**: An associate in the Miami office of Quintairos, Prieto, Wood & Boyer P.A. He practices in areas such as insurance defense, first-party homeowners\' claims, general litigation, automotive liability, product liability, and workers\' compensation defense. He received his Juris Doctor from Florida International University, College of Law.[4]\n*   **Sameer Mohammad (Broker)**: A previously registered broker with CRD#: 7953355, according to FINRA\'s BrokerCheck.[5]\n\nSources:\n[1] [researchgate.net](https://vertexaisearch.cloud.google.com/grounding-api-redirect/AUZIYQEpWVcp-RkenCWobTJWJp7xejXo8BLeHrKyfFpX8vJvW0ZJ0AfCjcRuoNCn1jTfvkK-kX2M1HVuAAw8PBpv7lKymNR_Vn_as4wXK7swBA4HjNVOtUZq1cFYxm3-XA_SILYx-VOJ7_7aymhe6_0ARw==)\n[2] [google.com](https://vertexaisearch.cloud.google.com/grounding-api-redirect/AUZIYQHS0oIe2oKlIFLbz-W6ylQL1hel_hAfBWgOhL_HaLY2I5PCrm6vFxfiPi5TE9MHgwDtRrBYL_eZ6wlSkzvK8AZRI_j3xhdmH4uO_TGjOyjQJ00TrZ-U2u2w3Mb521PVO1Xd5QOrjZutn_k7hxZ8WhJNnJkbWEwJ)\n[3] [uaeu.ac.ae](https://vertexaisearch.cloud.google.com/grounding-api-redirect/AUZIYQHNEP1X9zb