    summary: "Based on a web search for \"sameer-mohammad-19743b286\" OR \"sameer mohammad\" \"19743b286\" OR \"Sameer Mohammad\" \"sameer.912210@gmail.com\", several individuals named Sameer Mohammad or Muhammad Sameer were identified across various professions and locations:\n\n*   **Sameer Mohammed, Technology Leader & Author:** This individual is described as a technology leader, speaker, and author with over 25 years of experience in leading and delivering solutions across various industries. He holds a master\'s in computer science from the University of Bridgeport and is highly experienced in digital transformation, particularly with the Microsoft Power Platform. He is also the CIO and Co-founder of AQL Technologies and a Vice President at DeepVerse AI, as well as a member of the Forbes Technology Council.[1][2]\n*   **Muhammad Sameer, Fulbright Scholar:** Identified as a graduate student in Mechanical Engineering from Pakistan, currently a Fulbright Scholar at Rice University.[3]\n*   **Sameer Mohammad, Researcher (KAIMRC):** Affiliated with King Abdullah International Medical Research Centre (KAIMRC) in Riyadh, KSA, with research interests including insulin resistance and Type 2 Diabetes.[4]\n*   **Mohammed Sameer, Professional Boxer:** A professional boxer from the United Kingdom competing in the Middle division.[5]\n*   **Sameer Mohammad, UK Companies House:** Listed in the UK\'s Companies House records under personal appointments, indicating involvement with registered companies in the UK.[6]\n*   **Muhammad Sameer, Digital Creator & Marketing Professional:** A digital creator and marketing professional based in San Jose, CA, with extensive experience in helping brands grow through creative visuals, videos, and online strategies.[7]\n\nThe specific identifiers \"sameer-mohammad-19743b286\" and the email \"sameer.912210@gmail.com\" did not directly lead to unique profiles or additional information in the search results.\n\nSources:\n[1] [pmichicagoland.or