    thinking: "**Designing Experience Component**\n\nI\'m now focusing on designing the Experience component. I\'ve decided it will handle rendering timelines for both work experience and education. There will be a toggle at the top, allowing the user to switch between \"Work Experience\" and \"Education.\" This will help keep things organized and user-friendly. I\'m thinking about the best way to structure the data within the component.\n\n\n"
    modified_response: "I will create `/src/components/Experience.tsx` to handle career experience, education history, and certifications. It uses a side-by-side timeline split layout (Work History on the left, Education & Certifications on the right) on large screens, collapsing into a clean stacked timeline on smaller displays. Staggered scroll animations will guide the user through Sameer Mohammad\'s qualifications."
